freetype-py is an optional dependency

if you do not want to download files from internet
pass this option to setup.py  --no-download-t1-files
you can also add verbosity with --verbose option

t1 fontfiles can be found in this address
https://www.reportlab.com/ftp/pfbfer-20180109.zip

when installing extract the pfb fonts and install it to
usr/lib64/python3.9/site-packages/reportlab/fonts/
